usdSmdsAgent.name: usdSmdsAgent

revisions.description: Added support for major and sub interfaces.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdSmdsAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdSmdsAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Switched Multimegabit Data Service (SMDS) management component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdSmdsAgentV1.name: usdSmdsAgentV1
usdSmdsAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Switched Multimegabit Data Service (SMDS) management
        component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP agent.  This version of
        the SMDS component was supported in the Unisphere RX 3.1 thru 3.x system
        releases.
usdSmdsAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SMDS application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for major and sub interfaces

usdSmdsAgentV2.name: usdSmdsAgentV2
usdSmdsAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Switched Multimegabit Data Service (SMDS) management
        component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP agent.  This version of
        the SMDS component is supported in the Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent
        system releases.
usdSmdsAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SMDS application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
